Reasoning: The paper describes an integrated development environment (IDE) for enhancing productivity in contributing to sTeX based corpora. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) as it deals with software development tools. Additionally, the paper mentions support for context-aware command completion, module management, semantic macro retrieval, and theory graph navigation, which are all related to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The use of semantic annotations also suggests a connection to deep learning (cs.DL) and potentially cybernetics (cs.CY).
